{"TopicId":220551,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Suggestion: Tone down the purple on Eve","CreatedByName":"Periple","CreatedById":225622,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-01T08:59:29Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Periple","CreatedById":225622,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-01T08:59:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, Eve needs to be purple or it\u0027s not Eve, but does it have to be quite\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eso\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0purple?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI really liked the changes to the atmosphere and color palette on Laythe, making it still definitely Laythe but at the same time more like Titan. I think Eve could remain definitely Eve even if it was a little less overwhelmingly purple. As it currently stands it\u0027s a bit monotone and also makes all the craft look purple which isn\u0027t all that aesthetic. Maybe tone it down a little? This is VERY purple!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Lett\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022120.00\u0022 height=\u0022675\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/2167980409443280676/A330B2C3BA49565B8BED6D06C37642D4BD0908D8/?imw=5000\u0026amp;imh=5000\u0026amp;ima=fit\u0026amp;impolicy=Letterbox\u0026amp;imcolor=%23000000\u0026amp;letterbox=false\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vl3d","CreatedById":219348,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-01T09:35:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEve is in good hands. I trust everything blackrack and the team is gonna do with the planet atmospheric visuals. I\u0027m sure there are going to be a lot of improvements.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GluttonyReaper","CreatedById":59429,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-11-01T09:42:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCounterpoint: what if it was\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Emore\u00A0\u003C/em\u003Epurple?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Periple","CreatedById":225622,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-1